   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-1" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300064">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-1-a" mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>Guess I'll go get that orb, then.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>According to the research notes, the purification device is at Prayer's Resting Place. We need two items to activate it. A <FONT color=#a82424>White Purity Orb</FONT>, found in the innermost area of the <FONT color=#a82424>Sanctuary Core</FONT>. Along with a <FONT color=#a82424>Purification Device Key</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
