      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>After you get the <FONT color=#a82424>White Purity Orb</FONT>, you'll need the <FONT color=#a82424>Purification Device Key</FONT> next. Manticore Keruru, the guardian of the Purification Device, has that key.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
