      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>The <FONT color=#a82424>Purification Device Key</FONT> is at Prayer's Resting Place, but you need to get the <FONT color=#a82424>White Purity Orb</FONT> first. The orb is located at the innermost area of the <FONT color=#a82424>Sanctuary Core</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
